window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Lucien Thorne is the most vile monster in all of Thorngate. As Winter King, he rules our land with an iron fist and a cold, dead heart. And my father has just informed me that I am betrothed to marry him....</p> <p>As the Princess of Fall, it is my duty to marry whatever suitor my father chooses for me, but Lucien is not someone with whom I can fathom spending the rest of my life. Not even for duty.</p> <p>When he arrives to negotiate my dowry, I break protocol and take matters into my own hands. But the more time I spend with this mysterious man, the more I wonder if the rumors about him are even true.</p> <p>As I get to know the real Lucien, I start to discover that there is a dark history in his family, one that explains his ruthless behavior. One I plan to expunge if I am ever to live out my life in the Winter Palace in peace.</p> <p>As much as I want to hate Lucien Thorne and everything heâ€™s done to our realm...I cannot deny my heart.</p>"; 
